      "rule_type": "behavior",
      "text": "aboutToAppear 在创建自定义组件实例后、首次执行 build 之前调用。",
      "heading_path": ["自定义组件生命周期"],
      "dimension_ids": ["DIM-05"],
      "review_question_ids": ["RQ-lifecycle"],
      "tags": ["has_lifecycle"],
      "apis": ["aboutToAppear"],
      "domains": ["component-lifecycle"],
      "raw_keywords": ["首次构建"],
      "scenario": "自定义组件首次出现与首次构建的时序",
      "conditional_only": false,
      "applicability_note": "适用于自定义组件首次创建，不表示页面从后台返回时必然再次触发。",
      "risk_note": "不得把首次创建时机扩写成每次页面显示都会触发。",
      "review_status": "proposed"
    },
    {
      "rule_id": "OHDOC-E2E/LIFE-02",
      "target_tag": "has_lifecycle",
      "document_alias": "doc015",
      "source_span": {"start_line": 16, "end_line": 16},
      "source_span_sha256": "sha256:c75d7dc5b3c4bf7b8bdf2c74042fe56f2d02b75144d828c6d33ceac093a0158f",
      "rule_type": "constraint",
      "text": "aboutToDisappear 在自定义组件销毁前执行，其中禁止修改状态变量，尤其应避免修改 @Link。",
      "heading_path": ["自定义组件生命周期"],
      "dimension_ids": ["DIM-02", "DIM-05"],
      "review_question_ids": ["RQ-lifecycle", "RQ-state"],
      "tags": ["has_lifecycle", "has_state_management"],
      "apis": ["aboutToDisappear"],
      "decorators": ["@Link"],
      "domains": ["component-lifecycle", "state-management"],
      "raw_keywords": ["销毁前"],
      "scenario": "组件销毁回调中的状态修改",
      "conditional_only": true,
      "applicability_note": "仅当组件实际进入析构销毁流程时适用；隐藏或退后台本身不等于销毁。",
      "risk_note": "必须区分组件销毁、页面隐藏和应用退后台，避免把所有离开前台场景视为 aboutToDisappear。",
      "review_status": "proposed"
    },
    {
      "rule_id": "OHDOC-E2E/LIFE-03",
      "target_tag": "has_lifecycle",
      "document_alias": "doc015",
      "source_span": {"start_line": 59, "end_line": 59},
      "source_span_sha256": "sha256:c1651da3bde98be4fefc5e9196f09da63092bfd9ae02d4963ebe056aaedf7032",
      "rule_type": "guidance",
      "text": "不建议在 aboutToDisappear 中启动 async、Promise 或回调操作，否则闭包可能延长组件存活并阻止及时回收。",
      "heading_path": ["自定义组件生命周期", "自定义组件的删除"],
      "dimension_ids": ["DIM-06", "DIM-07"],
      "review_question_ids": ["RQ-concurrency", "RQ-lifecycle"],
      "tags": ["has_async", "has_lifecycle"],
      "apis": ["aboutToDisappear"],
      "domains": ["component-lifecycle", "resource-lifecycle"],
      "raw_keywords": ["垃圾回收"],
      "scenario": "组件销毁回调中的异步闭包",
      "conditional_only": true,
      "applicability_note": "需要确认异步操作位于 aboutToDisappear 且闭包会保留组件或相关状态。",
      "risk_note": "不能把所有已启动的异步操作直接判为泄漏，应检查捕获对象和持续时间。",
      "review_status": "proposed"
    },
    {
